1, 123.9874, 123.6898, 123.0109, 124.834, 125.4983, 125.2826, 126.918, 128.2541, 128.4133, 129.7881, 129.1072, 127.9132, 128.4371, 130.1515, 128.5346, 128.6317, 128.3708, 127.147, 127.0503, 126.1732, 125.6319, 125.4887, 126.0809, 125.0062, 125.4988, 125.9032, 125.899, 125.3433, 125.295, 125.3499, 125.3067, 125.1994, 124.8578, 124.9833, 125.0774, 124.4873, 124.7533, 124.4357, 124.2609, 124.0761, 123.6638, 123.0301, 123.5877, 123.8115, 123.9111, 124.1568, 124.3187, 123.1643, 122.9744, 123.8485, 122.404, 121.7675, 120.9608, 121.4438, 121.8921, 122.0857, 122.375, 121.5066, 121.2498, 121.1838, 120.8267, 120.463, 120.4462, 119.6941, 118.5791, 118.4174, 118.3378, 118.5367, 118.8158, 120.0619, 120.5079, 119.4619, 120.4118, 120.7396, 121.5836, 122.0763, 120.4993, 120.5771, 121.5036, 120.5721, 122.0036, 120.7634, 120.6385, 120.2303, 120.9794, 120.6967, 120.1114, 121.5846, 121.719, 121.9771, 123.0283, 124.5974, 125.145, 124.8455, 125.6849, 124.6098, 122.3869, 122.6393, 122.4352, 122.6087, 122.2932, 122.1742, 122.4062, 120.8533, 119.6789, 118.1198, 116.9872, 116.8474, 118.503, 120.1403, 119.4362, 119.5861, 120.1082, 120.0752, 119.1002, 119.0738, 118.5116, 118.7705, 117.2895, 118.5247, 117.0653, 118.629, 119.2617, 119.3215, 120.7426, 121.45, 120.8259, 121.1262, 120.6488, 119.8614, 119.2635, 118.5624, 118.745, 119.7628, 118.9559, 122.8734, 127.7947, 125.0891, 123.1376, 124.7736, 120.2399, 124.067, 124.4347, 120.9946, 119.9801, 115.7301, 123.6743, 122.4348, 124.6617, 113.5216, 118.1663, 113.6132, 114.5496, 111.7626, 112.0228, 112.7651, 110.6046, 111.1565, 111.1, 111.279, 111.5637, 112.3874, 112.3005, 114.552, 114.8747, 112.8997, 111.4876, 109.2153], "summary_html": "<h1>机构持仓（三）：机构偏好与因子构建</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>原报告在 A 股上发现\"机构持仓<strong>变化率</strong>\"因子比\"持仓水平\"更有效（提前增加率累计 9×）。移植到商品期货：用 <code>memberdiff20</code> (Top-20 会员净持仓) 作为机构定向信号代理，计算多窗口（10/21/63 日）EMA 平滑后变化，截面等权 rank 合成，top 30% long / bottom 30% short，21 日 rebalance。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.53</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>2.5%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.8%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-11.9%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.05</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.58</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.08</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>-0.25 / 1.07</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.02</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-2.01</span></td><td>1.77</td><td>0.86</td><td>1.82</td><td>0.81</td><td>0.88</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.16</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.44</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>memberdiff20</code></td><td>席位净持仓差</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每日</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>38.4%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>30.1</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\tilde D_{t,i}=\\text{EMA}_{21}(\\text{memberdiff20}_{t,i}),\\quad \\Delta_w \\tilde D_{t,i}=\\tilde D_{t,i}-\\tilde D_{t-w,i}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">C_{t,i}=\\frac{1}{3}\\sum_{w\\in\\{10,21,63\\}}\\text{CSrank}_t(\\Delta_w\\tilde D_{t,i})</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">s_{t,i}=\\begin{cases}+1&amp;C_{t,i}\\ge 0.7\\\\-1&amp;C_{t,i}\\le 0.3\\\\0&amp;\\text{else}\\end{cases},\\ w_{t,i}=s^{\\text{hold21}}_{t,i}/\\sum_j|s^{\\text{hold21}}_{t,j}|</div>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p>R1 (0.751): 12 变体覆盖 level/change/combo 家族；Δmemberdiff20 21d 最优；Δmember_all 负；level-short 负。<strong>发现：方向信号的变化率是主 alpha 源，非水平</strong>。 R2 (<strong>0.966 ✓</strong>, +29%): 弃 memall-change 家族；加多窗口 combo；10/21/63 等权 rank 突破 0.8。多窗口合成平滑单窗口噪声，ts_icir 0.085→0.332，后半 Sharpe 1.59 vs 前半 0.31。 R3 (0.966 持平): 5 种窗口组合 + 动量 combo + hold/quantile 变动全部无改进；top 10 变体均 ≥0.85，稳健。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li>daily 频率，全商品 (~57 主力)</li>\n<li>21 日 rebalance，gross-exposure 归一化</li>\n<li>T+1 开盘成交，单边 4bps</li>\n<li>关键发现: 机构持仓<strong>变化率</strong> (Δmemberdiff20) &gt; 水平。对比机构持仓（十二）分域 (Sharpe 0.82): 本报告用变化率直接得 0.97，动量 combo 增益有限 — 说明 Δmdiff 已捕捉\"机构流-趋势\" 效应。</li>\n<li>局限: 与既有 huachuan_diff 因子 corr 0.41 非冗余但相关，2019 早期负贡献（品种池稀疏），后续年度稳定。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>INST_W</code></td><td><code>21</code></td><td>EMA span for memberdiff20</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.9981</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.65s</li>\n</ul>"}